Beat milk and pudding mixes with whisk 2 min. Microwave 2 chocolate squares on HIGH 1 min. or until melted when stirred. Stir in 1 cup pudding; pour into crust. Add half the COOL WHIP and all but 3 Tbsp. candy to remaining pudding. Spoon over layer in crust. Top with remaining COOL WHIP and candy. Melt remaining chocolate square; drizzle over pie. Refrigerate 1 hour.